\end_inset

Second serve
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 
\emph default
may be announced
\emph on
.

\emph default
 The serving teammates do not switch sides, and Server 2 must send the ball
 into the service box diagonal from their current position on the court.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Once Server 2 faults, the ball goes to the opposing team to serve.
 
\emph on

